'''美國職業棒球大聯盟選秀聯盟'''（{{lang-en|MLB Draft League}}）為計畫於2021年開打的{{le|學院夏季棒球聯盟|Collegiate summer baseball}}<ref name=BDPresident/>。該聯盟由[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]及''Prep Baseball Report''建立，作為每年夏季{{le|美國職業棒球大聯盟選秀|MLB draft|大聯盟選秀}}中頂級選秀球員的展示場合<ref name=BDPresident/>。初期該聯盟將會有6支來自原[[美國職棒小聯盟|美國職棒小聯盟]]中{{le|紐約-賓州聯盟|New York–Penn League}}、[[東方聯盟|東方聯盟]]及[[卡羅萊納聯盟|卡羅萊納聯盟]]的球隊，經2021年小聯盟重組後納入該聯盟<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.milb.com/mahoning-valley/news/mahoning-valley-scrappers-retain-affiliation-with-major-league-baseball-in-new-m|title=Mahoning Valley Scrappers Retain Affiliation With Major League Baseball in New MLB Draft League|website=Mahoning Valley Scrappers|publisher=Minor League Baseball|date=November 30, 2020|access-date=November 30, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Cooper|first=J.J.|url=https://www.baseballamerica.com/stories/frederick-becomes-sixth-team-to-join-mlb-draft-league/|title=Frederick Becomes Sixth Team To Join MLB Draft League|website=Baseball America|date=December 9, 2020|access-date=December 9, 2020}}</ref>。該聯盟將會進行68場比賽，並會在包含大聯盟選秀在內的大聯盟明星賽系列活動期間休賽<ref name=MLBann>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/mlb-draft-league-to-begin-in-2021|title=MLB to Launch League for Draft Prospects|website=Major League Baseball|date=November 30, 2020|access-date=December 2, 2020}}</ref>。

